title: Microsoft office 2007.(S,E,G)
description:

*Microsoft Office Enterprise 2007
- Access 2007
- Excel 2007
- Groove 2007
- InfoPath 2007
- OneNote 2007
- Outlook 2007
- PowerPoint 2007
- Publisher 2007
- Word 2007
*Microsoft Office Visio Professional 2007
*Microsoft Office Project 2007
*Microsoft Expression Web (new FrontPage)

It also contains a launcher application I made myself 

The serials are written in by the launcher application, if there are problems they&#039;re also in the readme file inside the CD image.
All the products don&#039;t need activation, therefore you do not need a keygen, this is not a trial, it lasts forever .
